  "A ball's height is h = −16t² + 40t and a drone hovers at h = 24. When does the ball reach the drone's height?": "",
  "t = 1 and t = 1.5 seconds": "",
  "The ball never reaches that height": "",
  "t = 0 and t = 2.5 seconds": "",
  "t = 2.5 seconds only": "",
  "Set −16t² + 40t = 24: −16t² + 40t − 24 = 0. Divide by −8: 2t² − 5t + 3 = 0. Factor: (2t − 3)(t − 1) = 0, so t = 3/2 = 1.5 or t = 1. The ball reaches 24 feet on the way up (t = 1) and on the way down (t = 1.5).": "",
  "A water fountain arc follows y = −x² + 6x and a laser beam follows y = 2x + 3. At what points does the laser cross the water arc?": "",
  "No intersection": "",
  "(1, 5) and (3, 9)": "",
  "(2, 7) and (4, 11)": "",
  "(0, 3) only": "",
  "Set −x² + 6x = 2x + 3: −x² + 4x − 3 = 0, or x² − 4x + 3 = 0. Factor: (x − 1)(x − 3) = 0, so x = 1 or x = 3. When x = 1: y = 2(1) + 3 = 5. When x = 3: y = 2(3) + 3 = 9. Solutions: (1, 5) and (3, 9).": "",
  "A skateboarder's ramp follows y = 2x − 1 and a curved wall follows y = x² − 4. Where does the ramp meet the wall?": "",
